ements/chafta/Pages/australia-china-fta.aspx\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNB: NSW Trade &amp; Investment has developed its North Asia FTA Engagement Plan.\r\n\r\nThis will assist NSW businesses to take advantage of the opportunities from the Korean, Japanese and Chinese agreements.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Free Trade Agreements under negotiation:\r\n\r\n*Gulf Cooperation Council\r\n\r\n*Indonesia\r\n\r\n*India\r\n\r\n*Pacific Islands\r\n\r\nTrans-Pacific Partnerships (including Brunei Darussalam, Peru and Vietnam\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '(FTA)agreements', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '186-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-18 02:19:29', '2015-08-18 02:19:29', '', 186, 'http://trueaussiebrands.com/186-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
